  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. Specialized in dogfighting, this craft boasts superior mobility and advanced firepower, and is fitted with an upgraded <span class=\"name name-technology\">Positron Ejector</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，拥有卓越的机动性和先进的火力，专门用于空战。配备升级版<span class=\"name name-technology\">正电子冲击波</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。專門用來進行戰機纏鬥，此飛行器擁有超凡的機動性及優越的火力，並裝載升級版的<span class=\"name name-technology\">正電子發射器</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>皆可。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
